{"tid":1011680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子20年不洗生殖器還得性病　整支腐臭讓女醫治","createTime":"2019-02-07T03:30:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T15:17:02.000Z","uid":122,"like":120,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"7d689c2f50f268b768386b8e82d83c4a3c281080","tid":1011680,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190207/640_5600b694579fe8f2cef703fd4358e5ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190207%2F640_5600b694579fe8f2cef703fd4358e5ec.jpg&h=2ac486ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190207/640_a469e6d7ecd24452489d317181a98e69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190207%2F640_a469e6d7ecd24452489d317181a98e69.jpg&h=7d0f8525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國一個性治療節目，近日拍攝一個奇異案例，一名24歲男子札克(Zach)這輩子從來沒有好好清洗過自己的陰莖，甚至曾經得過性病，現在生殖器已經整支腐臭，並讓札克感到疼痛與不舒服。節目也請來女醫蘇頓(Naomi Sutton)，為札克好好治療。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，札克承認，自己洗澡的習慣非常草率，隨便把肥皂抹一抹，更因為覺得下體敏感，從來都不會仔細清洗生殖器，導致陰莖已出現腐臭的味道。札克也承認，曾經和小妹妹做愛後得到淋病。札克說，這6~9個月來生殖器出現疼痛感，而且已經無法正常收合。<br />\n<br />\n女醫蘇頓親手診治，認為札克罹患的是「包皮垢」(smegma)。很多網友與觀眾看到這一段，都感到不可思議，難以想像會有人長期以來不洗生殖器，髒到一個不行，完全沒有健康教育概念。但蘇頓說，在她治療的病患中，罹患包皮垢者不在少數，札克絕對不是唯一的患者。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190207/1513765\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190207%2F1513765&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=44638230\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190207%2F1513765&h=3b37099c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190207/1513765</a>"},{"pid":"a3be5d60dcd6233adebb7d3278f104320ec02422","tid":1011680,"