7e008306d96","tid":1011680,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e092d39c6c1f166c2e739bd99e8cb2f5852b3124","tid":1011680,"uid":144433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:08:52.000Z","msg":"其實點樣先清得乾淨<br />\n長遠黎講應該割包皮？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:11:39.000Z","msg":"反開佢洗 反唔開就要切"},{"pid":"331818121cd2c1859178a652b30806d0207efe56","tid":1011680,"uid":47954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190207/640_5600b694579fe8f2cef703fd4358e5ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190207%2F640_5600b694579fe8f2cef703fd4358e5ec.jpg&h=2ac486ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190207/640_a469e6d7ecd24452489d317181a98e69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190207%2F640_a469e6d7ecd24452489d317181a98e69.jpg&h=7d0f8525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國一個性治療節目，近日拍攝一個奇異案例，一名24歲男子札克(Zach)這輩子從來沒有好好清洗過自己的陰莖，甚至曾經得過性病，現在生殖器已經整支腐臭，並讓札克感到疼痛與不舒服。節目也請來女醫蘇頓(Naomi Sutton)，為札克好好治療。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，札克承認，自己洗澡的習慣非常草率，隨便把肥皂抹一抹，更因為覺得下體敏感，從來都不會仔細清洗生殖器，導致陰莖已出現腐臭的味道。札克也承認，<span style=\"color: red;\">曾經和小妹妹做愛</span>後得到淋病。札克說，這6~9個月來生殖器出現疼痛感，而且已經無法正常收合。<br />\n<br />\n女醫蘇頓親手診治，認為札克罹患的是「包皮垢」(smegma)。很多網友與觀眾看到這一段，都感到不可思議，難以想像會有人長期以來不洗生殖器，髒到一個不行，完全沒有健康教育概念。但蘇頓說，在她治療的病患中，罹患包皮垢者不在少數，札克絕對不是唯一的患者。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190207/1513765\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190207%2F1513765&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=44638230\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190207%2F1513765&h=3b37099c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190207/1513765</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes20.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes50.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes500.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6323f408e73603fb2c7b3ed33e687837284a9cc6","tid":1011680,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa31c143f0915a1da54915cb0772d4b68ac4586f","tid":1011680,"uid":66253,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"57c889e96b4cfe47c00b52f83767a77443509ff7","tid":1011680,"uid":34525,"like":69,"dislike":2,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:39:11.000Z","msg":"爛鳩都有人同佢做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:04:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:12:57.000Z","msg":"臭鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sor"},{"pid":"745a53426054b1f7e5c4f1fea79e4ae2e32a256e","tid":1011680,"uid":34854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"條片都睇唔到d鳩屎...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1f0c1091836e33538ef51a43a7f8d04b87629d","tid":1011680,"uid":232594,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:25:48.000Z","msg":"唔好比我含<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e89cbb1a5365081408f84184a1b183d13e06db","tid":1011680,"uid":26038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:25:56.000Z","msg